name: ANYTHING YOU SAY OR DO CAN AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU IN A TARGETED ADVERTISEMENT
description: From the "Think Privacy" series of privacy posters first launched in 2016 at the New Museum Store in NYC. From a total edition of 100. The first 50 editions were screenprinted. The second half are screenminted. Add 50 to the NFT edition number for the total adjusted edition number.
